longBusinessSummary: Earth Search Sciences, Inc., through its subsidiary, General Synfuels International, Inc., focuses on the development of technology for the extraction of oil and gas from oil shale. The company is headquartered in Lakeside, Montana.

Earth Search Sciences, Inc., through its subsidiary, General Synfuels International, Inc., focuses on the development of technology for the extraction of oil and gas from oil shale. The company is headquartered in Lakeside, Montana.
